#WATCHTHETHRONE turns 10🔥💿 A decade ago, Kanye West and Jay-Z released a collaboration album that marked music history forever.

Hit the link in bio to read about film maker Robert Lopuski’s incredible stories of documenting the ‘WTT’ sessions. [via @complexmusic]
